    • measureSystem

      public void measureSystem()
      Based on the probabilities of the system, this method will measure all qubits. When this method is called, the measuredValue value of every qubit contains a possible measurement value. The values are consistent for the entire system. (e.g. when an entangled pair is measured, its values are equal) However, different invocations of this method may result in different values.
